        "public int lastStoneWeight(int[] stones) {\n    PriorityQueue<Integer> pq=new PriorityQueue<>(Collections.reverseOrder());\n    for (int s:stones) pq.add(s);\n    while (pq.size()>1) {\n        int a=pq.poll(), b=pq.poll();\n        if (a!=b) pq.add(a-b);\n    }\n    return pq.isEmpty()?0:pq.peek();\n}",
