        "public int leastInterval(char[] tasks, int n) {\n    int[] freq=new int[26];\n    for (char t:tasks) freq[t-'A']++;\n    int maxF=Arrays.stream(freq).max().getAsInt();\n    int maxC=(int)Arrays.stream(freq).filter(f->f==maxF).count();\n    return Math.max(tasks.length,(maxF-1)*(n+1)+maxC);\n}",
